  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI would like to get the list of file in a folder for my tool : [forge-deploy](https://github.com/wighawag/forge-deploy)\r\n\r\nAs of now `forge-deploy` do not need `--ffi` and while I could use `--ffi` to read the folder myself, I would like to avoid `--ffi` if possible\r\n\r\nThere is currently cheatcodes to read files knowing their path, but there is no such thing for folders\r\n\r\nProposal:\r\n```\r\n// Reads the directory and return the list of file/folder in it as a list of string\r\nfunction readDir(string calldata) external returns (string[] memory);\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
